              {
                "type": "markdown",
                "id": "collect-automatic",
                "value": "### Automatically Collected\n\n**IP Addresses:** For security, spam prevention, and analytics\n\n**Browser Metrics:** Basic technical information (browser type, screen size, etc.) for site optimization\n\n**Usage Analytics:** Which pages you visit and how you navigate the site to improve user experience"
