              {
                "type": "markdown",
                "id": "collect-account",
                "value": "### Account Information\n\n**WebAuthn Keys:** Cryptographic keys stored on your device for secure, passwordless authentication\n\n**Content Contributions:** Your edits, ratings, and contributions to the encyclopedia (this is the point of the service!)"
              }
            ]
