              {
                "type": "markdown",
                "id": "choice-optional",
                "value": "All of the following are **completely optional** and only collected if you choose to provide them:\n\n**Email Address:** For account verification and important notifications (you control which ones)\n\n**Phone Number:** For additional account security (if you want it)\n\n**Professional Credentials:** Academic emails (.edu), professional profiles, or credentials for domain expertise verification\n\n**Profile Information:** Display name, bio, profile picture - whatever you want to share publicly\n\n**Personal Identification:** Only required for high-level verification (expert status) and handled with extreme care"
