              {
                "type": "markdown",
                "id": "use-purposes",
                "value": "**Running the Service:** Authentication, content management, preventing abuse\n\n**Quality Control:** Reputation system, content review, spam prevention\n\n**Site Improvement:** Understanding how users navigate and use OmniOntos\n\n**Communication:** Only for account security issues or service updates (if you provided an email)\n\n**Verification:** Confirming expertise for domain authority (only if you request it)"
