                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "markdown",
                "id": "dont-list",
                "value": "**No Selling:** We never sell, rent, or trade your personal information\n\n**No Tracking:** No third-party tracking or advertising cookies\n\n**No Spam:** We don't send marketing emails or share your contact info\n\n**No Snooping:** We don't read your private messages or monitor your device\n\n**No Permanent Storage:** You can delete your account at any time, contributions will remain under the CC0 1.0 Universal License"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "markdown",
            "id": "your-rights",
            "value": "## Your Rights\n\n**Access:** See what information we have about you\n\n**Correction:** Update or correct your information\n\n**Deletion:** Delete your account and associated data\n\nControl:** Manage your privacy settings and verification level\n\nTo exercise these rights, simply contact us or use the account settings page."
          },
          {
            "type": "markdown",
            "id": "security",
            "value": "## Security\n\nWe use industry-standard security measures:\n\n- **WebAuthn** for passwordless, phishing-resistant authentication\n- **Encrypted connections** (HTTPS) for all data transmission\n- **Secure servers** with regular security updates\n- **Limited access** - only authorized staff can access user data\n- **Regular backups** with encryption at rest"
          },
          {
            "type": "markdown",
            "id": "changes",
            "value": "## Changes to This Policy\n\nWe'll notify users of any significant privacy policy changes through:\n\n- Site announcements for all users\n- Email notifications (if you provided an email)\n- At least 30 days notice before changes take effect\n\nMinor clarifications may be made without notice, but the core principles won't change without community input."
          },
